reviewText: In this vol. Ren continues her torment of Takeya.  There's some history and drama to do with both Miu and Neneko in this vol.  Finally it rounds out with a fun bath house episode.  There are series with better story line but very few that pack in this much fun and comedy.  If you like the first two vols you'll love the rest!
As usual, I love this series. This volume a lot, because it includes an unaired episode! English and japanese audio, also with english subtitles! Enjoy it! I sure did!
